{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"14":"Fasting (Kitab Al-Siyam)"},"section_detail":{"14":{"hadithnumber_first":2313,"hadithnumber_last":2476,"arabicnumber_first":2313,"arabicnumber_last":2476}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2450,"arabicnumber":2450,"text":"حدثنا ابو كامل، حدثنا ابو داود، حدثنا شيبان، عن عاصم، عن زر، عن عبد الله، قال كان رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يصوم - يعني من غرة كل شهر - ثلاثة ايام","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":14,"hadith":138}}]}